Europa Universalis IV: Cradle of Civilization (c) Paradox Development Studio
Release Date: 11/2017 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Simulation

The fertile valleys and trade routes of the Middle East have
attracted ambitious conquerors since the beginning of recorded
history. Now,Europa Universalis IVadds greater depth and more
varied possibilities to this crossroads of empires in the new
expansionCradle of Civilization. With new decisions and
opportunities tied to the historical development of the region in
the early modern era,Cradle of Civilizationfurther enhances the
award-winning grand strategy ofEuropa Universalis IV

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/721340/

to run this game with admin privileges instead
